<p>Casual players have begged for an alternate upgrade path from raiding.  This expansion offers that in spades.  For the first time in a long time, I've been able to upgrade 4-5 pieces of my gear without having to spend megahours repeating the same old tired missions.  Not only that, but I've only explored a portion of the zones that are available to me.</p>

<p>Casual players asked that not all zones be locked up.  With this expansion, only one zone is locked.  Everyone is free to group in almost every single zone provided.  That provides everyone with more freedom to do more things.   If you are 65 and cannot find anything to do in this expansion, then you are correct.  You should leave the game.<br />
