<p>I wasn't arguing with you at all loral, but I will say that a LOT of the fols I know who consider themselves "non-raiders" still raid, now whether that is choice or lack of options, I will leave up to the individual to decide.  I am not arguing that EQ doesn't need to be fun throughout, but it is ultimately a leveling treadmill, and I think SOE has done a remarkable job at continuing the treadmill past the top end.  I ultimately think things like TLC and required levels should have been put in from the start and AA never should have come into the game, and instead people should have continued to "level on up." to 100 or beyond.</p>

