<p class="posted"><strong>Posted by <a target="_blank" title="http://www.stormhammer.org/forums" href="http://mobhunter.com/mt/mobhunter_post21.cgi?__mode=red;id=286">Naladini</a> at September 29, 2004 11:12 PM</strong></p>
<p>"The majority of players under 50 statistic includes active players and excludes bazaar mules. The majority of active characters are under level 50. I don't know exactly what defines "active" but probably logging on once a week counts.</p>

<p>This does not mean, however, that they play the most amount of time. I bet the most amount of time online goes to 65+ characters. However, time online or not, we all pay the same price.<br />
